she's going to talk a little bit about functional genomics and drug screening for

24
00:01:13.260 --> 00:01:15.660
precision medicine in acute leukemia.

25
00:01:16.400 --> 00:01:20.120
Whereas, Dr. Woyach is the director of the

26
